WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.000
The animated Manta Transit logo appears over a background showing the city skyline.

00:00:02.000 --> 00:00:04.000
An animated hand types a destination into the app's search bar on a phone screen.

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:06.000
An animated map highlights the best route, connecting a walking icon and a bus icon with a line.

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:08.000
A bus icon moves in real time along the map next to a live location marker.

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:10.000
The closing screen shows the Manta Transit logo with the slogan "your city in motion".
